These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, collecting, photography, writing, puzzles, board-games, filmmaking
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, oliveros, davidoff, blend, dunhill, bongani, cain
 1. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is photography##8
 3. the old-henry-smoker is not to the left of the oliveros-smoker##8
 4. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is not the oliveros-smoker##6
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 9. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##7
10. the oliveros-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
12. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
13. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##7
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
16. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
17. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
18. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the davidoff-smoker##1
19. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
20. the person who's hobby is writing is not the bongani-smoker##6
21. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
22. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Hobby           | board-games | photography | filmmaking | collecting  | puzzles  | writing | baking    |
| Cigar   | oliveros   | old-henry   | davidoff   | blend | dunhill | cain        | bongani |

