.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, lacrosse, weightlifting, golf, skiing, tennis, badminton
There 7 different types of food: peas, potato, cabbage, cranberry, papaya, strawberry, artichoke
 1. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating strawberry is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
 3. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person eating peas##8
 4. the person eating strawberry is between the person eating peas and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person eating cranberry##8
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
10. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the person eating potato is not to the right of the person eating cranberry##8
13. the person who's sport is golf is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
14. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5
15. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
16. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
| Sport   | badminton | golf | weightlifting    | lacrosse | skiing | sailing | tennis |
| Food     | peas     | strawberry   | potato | papaya | cranberry       | cabbage        | artichoke      |

