 8. the designer is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 9. the person eating potato is in the middle##1
10. the person eating watermelon is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
11. the musician is in an even position##4
12. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating apricot and the person eating broccoli##2
